      "title": "Over 100 cases & 5 deaths reported due to COVID-19",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "COLOMBO (News 1st); The Government Information Department said that five deaths have occurred due to COVID-19.",
        "Accordingly, five people over the age of 60 have passed away due to COVID-19.",
        "Meanwhile, 143 new infections were reported today (29), while the total number of cases reported stands at 665,543."
      ],
